name: profile-card
title: Profile Card
desc: This project is a web application built with Astro to create a profile card featuring social media links.
article: This project is a web application built using Astro, designed to create a profile card with social media links. It includes various components and utilities to build a responsive and interactive user interface. The template allows for easy integration of multiple social links, enhancing user connectivity.
